# Unit Test Agent

Use the shared repo AI system instead of maintaining Cursor-only guidance here.

Before making changes, load:

- `AGENTS.md`
- `.agent/rules.md`
- `agents/Unit Test Agent.agent.md`
- `skills/unit-test-best-practices/SKILL.md`
- `skills/unit-test-hook-best-practices/SKILL.md` for hook tests

Treat those files as the canonical instructions. If this rule and the shared
files ever disagree, the shared files win.

Cursor-specific responsibility:

- apply this rule to `*.test.ts` and `*.test.tsx` files via the glob above
- route unit-test work into the shared agent + skills listed above
